channel.title: Emote tabs teleport?
channel.description: Hi I'm using Allstar Scape source and im trying to figure out how to make emote tabs teleport to places. I looked for a tut and the only one i found was a shitty one that only replaced an old emote tab. I need to make a new tab that teleports. Thanks.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: August 13, 2008, 06:44:57 pm[/size][hr]Plz I Need help

item.title: Emote tabs teleport?
item.dc:creator: @modbrian modbrian
item.description:
@modbrian wrote:

ya when you put your mouse over the emote tab you want to change up in the top left corner it will say a number, search that number in your client.java, say the number is like 163 search case 163.
then just change the coords.

if you want to change the name of the tab from something like teampk to something else open your texthandler and search the name you want to change, then jsut replace it with the new name.
